title: Difficult to Spot AI Losers: Dudley
description: Franklin Templeton Senior Investment Strategist Katrina Dudley discusses the latest jobs report, market broadening and the difficulty in spotting the AI losers versus winners. She speaks to Bloomberg's Matt Miller and Dani Burger on 'Open Interest.' (Source: Bloomberg)
